#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*5.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    vec3 p,r=iResolution,c=vec3(0),
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,.7));
    float i=0.,s,e,g=0.,t=-iTime;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        p=R(g*d,normalize(H(t*1.1)),0.);

    p.xy*=mat2(cos(iTime),sin(iTime),-sin(iTime), cos(iTime));
        p=asin(.7*sin(p));
        s=2.5+sin(.5*t+3.*sin(t*2.))*.5;

        for(int i=0;i++<6;p=p*e-vec3(2.2,.5+cos(iTime*0.1),3.5))
            p=abs(p),

            p=p.x<p.y?p.zxy:p.zyx,
              p=p.y<p.z?p.xzy:p.xyz,
                p=p.y<p.z?p.xzy:p.xyz,

            s*=e=2.0;

        g+=e=abs(length(p.xzxz)-.13)/s+2e-5;
	    c+=mix(vec3(1),H(p.z*.5+t*.1),.4)*.02/exp(.5*i*i*e);
	}
	c*=c;
    O=vec4(c,1);
}
